 Troye Sivan 在“Rush”视频中回应身体多样性批评https://www.nme.com/news/music/troye-sivan-responds-to-body-diversity-criticism-in-rush-video-3470533?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=troye-sivan-responds-to-身体多样性批评热潮视频Kyann-Sian WilliamsWed, 19 Jul 2023 18:06:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3470533 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我确实听到了批评”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/troye-sivan-responds-to-body-diversity-criticism-in-rush-video-3470533">Troye Sivan 在“Rush”视频中回应身体多样性批评的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/troye-sivan-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/troye-sivan">特洛伊·希文 (Troye Sivan)</a>回应了他最近因复出单曲《Rush》的音乐视频中缺乏身体多样性而受到的强烈反对。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/troye-sivan-bloom-review-2371541">Troye Sivan – “Bloom”评论</a></li></ul><p>上周，这位澳大利亚流行歌星推出了《Rush》，同时宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/troye-sivan-announces-new-album-something-to-give-each-other-single-rush-listen-preorder-3468192">他五年来的第一张专辑《Something To Give Each Other》</a> 。主打单曲的音乐视频粗俗又性感，但在网上受到了批评，因为许多人认为缺乏身体多样性——该剪辑的主角是骨瘦如柴且大部分是白人。</p><p> “我确实听到了批评，”他告诉<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/culture/pride/troye-sivan-responds-rush-music-video-criticism-1235373815/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公告牌</a></em>。 “说实话，这不是我们的想法——我们显然不是说，‘我们希望视频中出现一种特定类型的人。’我们只是制作了视频，并没有考虑太多。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Troye Sivan - Rush（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/b53QJYP-lqY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位 28 岁的年轻人还提到了<a href="https://www.vulture.com/2023/07/troye-sivan-rush-review.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vulture</em></a>的一篇关于“Rush”的评论，其中包括许多人认为对瘦人有害的评论。 “他们在谈论[身体缺乏多样性]，在同一句话中，这个人说，‘吃点东西，你们这些愚蠢的年轻人，’”他说。</p><p> “读到这篇文章真的让我很沮丧——因为我对自己的身体形象也有不安全感。我认为每个人的身体都一样美丽，包括我自己的身体，看到人们谈论别人的身体真是太糟糕了。”</p><p>在有关该视频的新闻稿中，这位歌手说：“在舞池上亲吻一个满头大汗的陌生人的感觉，两个小时的约会变成了一个周末，一次暗恋，一个冬天，一个夏天。一场又一场的派对，一场又一场的派对。我所有的经历都来自于我感到自信、自由和解放的章节。独立，但在某种程度上与我周围的音乐和社区联系最紧密。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CuowUIELdet/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% -