扎威·阿什顿透露了她从未婚夫汤姆·希德勒斯顿那里得到的漫威建议https://www.nme.com/news/film/zawe-ashton-reveals-marvel-advice-she-got-from-fiance-tom-hiddleston-3470624?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=zawe-ashton-reveals-她从未婚夫汤姆·希德勒斯顿那里得到的惊奇建议Will RichardsWed, 19 Jul 2023 17:57:51 +0000 Film NewsNewsMarvel https://www.nme.com/?p=3470624 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奇迹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该演员在《奇迹》中饰演达本 (Dar-Ben)</p><p>扎威<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/zawe-ashton-reveals-marvel-advice-she-got-from-fiance-tom-hiddleston-3470624">·阿什顿 (Zawe Ashton) 透露她从未婚夫汤姆·希德勒斯顿 (Tom Hiddleston) 那里得到的漫威建议的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奇迹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>扎威·阿什顿透露了她的未婚夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hiddleston">汤姆·希德勒斯顿</a>给她的关于为漫威工作的建议。</p><p>阿什顿在新片<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-marvels"><em>《漫威》</em></a>中饰演达本，她的搭档曾在多部漫威作品中饰演洛基。</p><p>阿什顿告诉<em><a href="https://ew.com/movies/the-marvels-zawe-ashton-tom-hiddleston-villain-advice/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《娱乐周刊》</a></em> ：“这引发了一些令人难以置信的对话，谈论他在这支球队十多年来的经历。”</p><p> “我们谈话的主要收获之一是：‘你投入漫威的东西，你就会得到回报。’”他说：“如果你怀着开放的心态和良好的职业道德进入这个领域，并且只想为粉丝提供令人惊叹的体验，那么你将在这些场景中获得令人惊叹的体验。”他确实以这种方式赋予了我力量。”</p><p>这位<em>《鲜肉》</em>明星补充道：“他还提出了一些非常好的实用建议，那就是：确保你有足够的拉链，可以穿着服装去洗手间。我现在意识到，这是一个非常好的建议。” </p><figure id="attachment_2879220" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2879220" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2879220" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230.jpg" alt="惊奇队长" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1268578230-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2879220" class="wp-caption-text"> Zawe Ashton 于 2020 年 2 月伦敦时装周。图片来源：Kirstin Sinclair/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-marvels-has-been-delayed-by-four-months-poster-brie-larson-3400923"><em>《漫威》</em>推迟了四个月</a>。尼亚·达科斯塔 (Nia DaCosta) 执导的 2019 年<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/captain-marvel-film-review-2457783-2457783">《惊奇队长》</a></em>续集原定于 7 月 28 日上映，但现在将于 11 月 10 日上映。</p><p> <em>《漫威》</em>也是 2021 年<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/wandavision">《旺达与幻视》</a></em>和 2022 年<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/ms-marvel">《惊奇女士》</a>的后续作品。</em></p><p> <em>《漫威》</em>的剧情简介如下：“在<em>漫威女士</em>的事件发生后，卡罗尔·丹弗斯/惊奇队长（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brie-larson">布丽·拉尔森饰</a>）、漫威女士/卡玛拉·汗（伊曼·韦拉尼饰）和光谱/莫妮卡·兰博（泰柔娜·帕里斯饰）开始交换位置每次他们使用自己的力量时，都必须互相合作，找出原因。”</p><p><em>漫威</em>还将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">塞缪尔·L·杰克逊</a>主演，这是他第十五次出演尼克·弗瑞，与漫威新人阿什顿一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/zawe-ashton-star-villain-captain-marvel-2-2879210">出演主要反派</a>。</p><p>扎威<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/zawe-ashton-reveals-marvel-advice-she-got-from-fiance-tom-hiddleston-3470624">·阿什顿 (Zawe Ashton) 透露她从未婚夫汤姆·希德勒斯顿 (Tom Hiddleston) 那里得到的漫威建议的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
